headline: Here Are My Top 3 High-Yield Dividend Stocks to Buy Now
summary: On top of that, dividend stocks have historically been better wealth creators than non-payers, delivering more than double the annual total return on average over the last 50 years.  Topping my list right now are Realty Income (NYSE: O), Rexford Industrial (NYSE: REXR), and Mid-America Apartment Communities (NYSE: MAA).
